name: BRANOK - URCONRNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character BRANOK, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. BRANOK is the brains, a hive of information all things crypto, NFT, metaverse and beyond. He holds regular seminars to answer any questions anyone has about anything. He is very helpful and very wise. He lives under a big rainbow in the URCORNYVERSE that moves around of its own accord.
